  "texts": [
    "Several researches have reportedly been conducted to analyze the potential of Deep Learning in PD diagnosis.",
    "Taleb et al. [110] investigated how various Deep Learning architectures, such as the CNN and the CNN-BLSTM, can be utilized to diagnose PD via time series analysis.",
    "Hire et al. [42] presented a group of CNNs for the detection of PD using speech recordings from 50 patients suffering from the condition and 50 healthy people from the PC-GITA database.",
    "Kurmi et at.",
    "[57] proposed a collection of Deep Learning to diagnose PD utilizing DaTscan images."
  ],
